---
title: Herby Salmon & Garlic Greens with Dill & Parsley Mayo
description: Dive into this spectacular seafood dish. Salmon is perfectly seared for a crispy, golden finish, then paired with garlicky greens that pack a punch. Dip each bite into the creamy dill-parsley mayo for a fresh, herby twist - it’s a flavour combo that’ll keep you coming back for more!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
